snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Your Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Stories don't write themselves. Legends do. Step into World Tour with your avatar to meet the legendary characters who will inspire your journey in finding the meaning of true strength.

Street Fighter 6 hits the scene on June 2 on PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X|S, and Steam. A new era is about to begin.

Pre-order Now - https://streetfighter.com/6/en-us/product/
Download the Demo - https://streetfighter.com/6/en-us/demo/

#StreetFighter6 #Capcom #WorldTour #Ryu #ChunLi #Ken
